<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Telemetry: send plan-utilization samples on every refresh, even when history storage does not change (flat usage previously skipped the pipeline after the July 5 main merge).</li>
<li>Ollama: adopt upstream cookie-access error surfacing so the macOS app reports Keychain/Full Disk Access issues instead of a generic missing-session message.</li>
</ul>
